text: Edin Prljača (born 26 April 1971) is a Bosnian professional football manager and former football goalkeeper. He was most recently the sporting director of Bosnian Premier League club Čelik Zenica. ==References== ==External links== *Edin Prljača at Soccerpunter Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Sarajevo Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina footballers Category:FK Sarajevo players Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina football managers Category:Premier League of Bosnia and Herzegovina managers Category:FK Sarajevo managers Category:FK Olimpik managers Category:NK Travnik managers Category:NK Čelik Zenica managers
